You will need a proxy to make this work.  If you're on a mac, add a vhost to your local apache that looks like this:



<VirtualHost *:80>
   DocumentRoot "/Library/WebServer/Documents/weatherrob"
   ServerName weatherrob.local

   AcceptPathInfo On

   ProxyPass /api/weather/ http://weather.yahooapis.com/
   ProxyPassReverse /api/weather http://weather.yahooapis.com/

   ProxyPass /api/where/ http://where.yahooapis.com/
   ProxyPassReverse /api/where/ http://where.yahooapis.com/

   <Directory /Library/WebServer/Documents/weatherrob>
        Options Indexes FollowSymLinks MultiViews
        AllowOverride All
        Order allow,deny
        allow from all
   </Directory>

</VirtualHost>
